Output plugin-install.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1000
Set Height 520
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type `export CLAUDE_CONFIG_DIR=$(mktemp -d) && clear`
Enter
Sleep 1s
Show

Type "claude plugin marketplace add eugeniughelbur/obsidian-second-brain"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 12s

Type "claude plugin install obsidian-second-brain@obsidian-second-brain"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 10s

Type "claude plugin list"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

Sleep 3s
